  "name": "RPlog_The_Day_After",
  "title": "The Day After",
  "summary": "At dawn on a beach, Paul Nighman wakes beside Jessalyn after a night together, and the two share a tender, passionate, and emotionally fraught morning. Jessalyn, fearful of his impending departure and burdened by old griefs, weeps and confesses she partly used him to forget another man, wounding Paul before he reassures her that the night was no mistake. Their melancholy gives way to playful flirtation and a splashing tussle in the surf before they return to the barracks to clean up and avoid notice. Later, Jessalyn slips away without a goodbye, and Paul waits at an outdoor cafe, where the sardonic woman Ariana, a witness to his humiliating cantina experience on Tatooine, needles him about his past and his vulnerabilities. Their exchange turns sharp and cold, and Ariana departs after warning the guarded Corellian to be less open about his weaknesses, leaving Paul angry and unsettled by how raw his new emotions have become.",
